  "templates": [
    {
      "id": "outreach-cold",
      "name": "Guest Outreach — Cold",
      "category": "Pre-Production",
      "template": "Subject: Would love to have you on Retail AI Transformation\n\nHi {{guestName}},\n\nI'm Rishabh, CEO of FERMÀT Commerce. We're launching a podcast called Retail AI Transformation — conversations with operators making the change.\n\nI'd love to have you on because {{whyGreat}}.\n\nThe format is conversational — 25-35 minutes, recorded on Riverside. We'd explore {{topicIdea}}.\n\nWould you be open to a quick call to discuss?\n\nBest,\nRishabh"
    },
    {
      "id": "outreach-warm",
      "name": "Guest Outreach — Warm Intro",
      "category": "Pre-Production",
      "template": "Subject: Podcast conversation — {{topicIdea}}\n\nHi {{guestName}},\n\n{{mutualConnection}} suggested I reach out. I'm launching a podcast on enterprise retail AI transformation and your work at {{guestCompany}} is exactly the kind of operator perspective our audience needs.\n\nThe format is relaxed — 25-35 min conversation, not a formal interview. I'd love to explore {{topicIdea}} with you.\n\nWould you have 15 minutes this week for a quick pre-call?\n\nBest,\nRishabh"
    },
    {
      "id": "guest-prep-brief",
      "name": "Guest Prep Brief",
      "category": "Pre-Production",
      "template": "# Guest Prep Brief — Episode {{episodeNumber}}\n\n**Guest:** {{guestName}}, {{guestTitle}} at {{guestCompany}}\n**Recording Date:** {{recordingDate}}\n**Format:** Conversational interview, 25-35 minutes on Riverside\n\n## What to Expect\n- Rishabh will lead the conversation — no script, just natural discussion\n- We'll cover: {{topicIdea}}\n- Feel free to share specific examples, data, or stories from your experience\n- Recording will be edited before publishing (we cut awkward pauses, filler, etc.)\n\n## Logistics\n- **Platform:** Riverside.fm (link will be sent 24 hours before)\n- **Audio:** Use headphones + quiet room for best quality\n- **Video:** Camera on preferred but not required\n- **Duration:** Plan for 40 minutes total (5 min setup + 30 min conversation + 5 min buffer)\n\n## Discussion Topics\n1. {{keyQuestion}}\n2. Your journey to {{guestCompany}} and the AI transformation you're leading\n3. What's working vs. what's harder than expected\n4. Advice for other enterprise retailers starting this journey\n5. What you're betting on for the next 12 months"
    },
    {
      "id": "rishabh-prep",
      "name": "Rishabh Recording Prep",
      "category": "Pre-Production",
      "template": "# Recording Prep — {{episodeTitle}}\n\n**Guest:** {{guestName}} ({{guestCompany}})\n**Date:** {{recordingDate}}\n\n## Guest Background\n- [Research to be filled by Sophie]\n\n## Thesis Connection\nThis episode connects to: {{thesisPoints}}\n\n## Key Question\n{{keyQuestion}}\n\n## Suggested Opener\n\"{{guestName}}, you're at the center of something interesting at {{guestCompany}} — [specific thing]. What made you bet on AI when most enterprise retailers were still skeptical?\"\n\n## Talking Points\n1. Their AI transformation journey — what triggered the shift\n2. {{topicIdea}}\n3. What's surprised them most\n4. Where they disagree with conventional wisdom\n5. What they'd tell their peers who haven't started yet\n\n## Lightning Round\n- Most underrated AI use case in retail?\n- One thing you'd do differently if starting over?\n- Prediction for retail AI in 2027?"
    },
    {
      "id": "show-notes",
      "name": "Show Notes / Episode Description",
      "category": "Publishing",
      "template": "# Episode {{episodeNumber}}: {{episodeTitle}}\n\n{{guestName}}, {{guestTitle}} at {{guestCompany}}, joins Rishabh to discuss {{topicIdea}}.\n\n## What We Cover\n- {{keyPoint1}}\n- {{keyPoint2}}\n- {{keyPoint3}}\n\n## About the Guest\n{{guestName}} is {{guestBio}}.\n\n## Links\n- {{guestLinkedIn}}\n- FERMÀT Commerce: https://www.fermatcommerce.com\n- Subscribe: [Apple Podcasts] [Spotify] [YouTube]\n\n## Timestamps\n- 0:00 — Intro\n- 2:00 — {{topic1}}\n- 10:00 — {{topic2}}\n- 20:00 — {{topic3}}\n- 28:00 — Lightning round"
    },
    {
      "id": "linkedin-teaser",
      "name": "LinkedIn — Teaser Post (Rishabh)",
      "category": "Promotion",
      "template": "{{hookLine}}\n\nI sat down with {{guestName}} from {{guestCompany}} to talk about {{topicIdea}}.\n\nOne thing that stood out:\n\n→ {{keyInsight}}\n\nFull episode drops {{publishDate}}.\n\n{{listenLink}}"
